name: imp Album & T-shirt bundle
description:
CD copy of imp's debut album Moon Coastal Maine plus an imp t-shirt for only £15.

Moon Coastal Maine is released on 25th November and costs £8 when bought separately at http://philophobiamusic.bandcamp.com/album/moon-coastal-maine

There are two different t-shirt designs. One white t-shirt with an image of 'Yousaf' in black. The other is black with the imp pyramid logo in orange. Both can be seen and purchased separately for £10 at http://impworld.bigcartel.com

Bundle will ship on or before the album's release date of 25th November.

name: Philophobia Music Bundle
description:
2013 marked Philophobia Music's fifth anniversary. 

To mark the occasion we made this T-shirt with all the front covers of our releases of the first five years. 

We also released a compilation entitled 'We PHOPPED Something In The Water' featuring 20 new tracks from bands from our roster.

Tracklisting
1. I Can't Help Myself - Runaround Kids
2. Viktoria Plzen - Piskie Sits
3. Love's Just A Feeling - Buen Chico
4. Ocean - Fur Blend
5. Ubelter - Protectors
6. Pregnant - SLUGS
7. Friends With Girls - The Spills
8. Feel Anything - Jack Winn
9. Home It's Not The Heart - Shake Your Halo Down
10. Bone Head - SWORDS
11. Finalised - Tiny Planets
12. Miss Most Mornings - the Michael Ainsley Band
13. Hard To See - The Do's
14. Sometimes Life's Cool - Mi Mye
15. Salt Lips - We Are Losers
16. Haunted Stadiums - Yard Wars
17. C/Beam - One Day, After School... 
18. Elephant Man, Elegant Woman - imp
19. You Fell, You Fell, You Fell - Clandestines
20. Vacancies - St Gregory Orange

Get both along with To Dare Is To Do EP. The 6 track compilation EP features 2 tracks each by 3 different artists - Above Us The Waves, Gary Gore & E.E. Viles and Daniel Lancaster. Each artist also featured on their own 3" CD in a handmade package.

Tracklisting
Disc A
1. X-Ray Eyes - Above Us The Waves
2. The Woods - Above Us The Waves

Disc B
1. Decades Erased - Gary Gore & E.E. Viles
2. Turns Green - Gary Gore & E.E. Viles

Disc C 
1. Square One - Daniel Lancaster
2. And Her Absent Mask - Daniel Lancaster

ONLINE OFFER ONLY. AVAILABLE WHILST STOCKS LAST.

name: Bitching Cassettes Bundle
description:
Our cassette imprint Bitching Cassettes has been quiet this year (largely because we've been so busy on the Philophobia side of things) but expect new things next year. In the meantime you can get a Bitching Cassettes logo t-shirt together with the split Runaround Kids & The Spills cassingle. 

The cassette is limited to 100 copies and only a small handful remain. It also comes with a download code.

The T-shirt is black only and available in small, medium and large.

name: Philophobia 1st 5 Years T-shirt
description:
Brand new t-shirt celebrating the 5th anniversary of our first release. It features the front cover of every Philophobia Music release during our first five years. All listed chronologically and shaped into our heart shaped logo.

Expected 26th July.

Design by Laura Alice.
